{"tid":1747633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「緊急」「行動Post」投票日有行動！ 要人一齊參與 廉潔行動！","createTime":"2019-11-23T10:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:46:48.000Z","uid":84632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5617653b2d048151b7f00f8c8d05749ecc011e8a","tid":1747633,"uid":84632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23KkyDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23KkyDo.jpg&h=1758f9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下行動內容與 廉政公署 完全無關<br />\n純屬大家自發宣傳廉潔資訊<br />\n維護公平選舉<br />\n正如廉署口號：<br />\n香港勝在有你同ICAC<br />\n杜選賄選，人人有責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廉潔行動 全民反種票 反賄選<br />\n日期：11月24日（星期日）<br />\n時間：7:30am &ndash; 10:30pm （愈早開始愈有效）<br />\n服飾：淺色恤衫 深色西褲（專業形象）（唔怕熱可以著埋件西裝褸）<br />\n<br />\n行動：<br />\n影印一大堆廉署宣傳單張<br />\n例如： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/10_live_l.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_281%2F10_live_l.jpg&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=a44beeef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/10_live_l.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/2011_election_api_poster_l.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_281%2F2011_election_api_poster_l.jpg&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=f4329f3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/2011_election_api_poster_l.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/11_growth_l.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_281%2F11_growth_l.jpg&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=1c45cc95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/11_growth_l.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/2012eggl.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_281%2F2012eggl.png&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=7080fbcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/2012eggl.png</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/2015apil.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_281%2F2015apil.png&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=e6d2111a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/filemanager/tc/content_281/2015apil.png</a><br />\n（更多選擇： <a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/resource/mmu/poster/p19/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fresource%2Fmmu%2Fposter%2Fp19%2Findex.html&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=a1ebae32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/resource/mmu/poster/p19/index.html</a> <br />\n少數族裔語言都有： <a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/resource/publications-and-videos/na/index.html）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fresource%2Fpublications-and-videos%2Fna%2Findex.html%EF%BC%89&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=88edce6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/resource/publications-and-videos/na/index.html）</a><br />\n<br />\n主動派發畀去投票嘅市民<br />\n當然包括疑似想進行賄選 / 種票 / 掌心雷 等等嘅公公婆婆叔叔嬸嬸<br />\n眼神堅定地提醒佢哋：<br />\n「唔好收完禮物去投票報答人，廉政公署實查到，走唔甩」<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n1）千祈唔好冒充廉署人員！<br />\n真係唔好！呢個一定犯法，而且完全冇需要。<br />\n著西裝恤衫西褲已經好夠，最緊要感覺可信。<br />\n<br />\n2）唔好阻住人哋去投票！<br />\n呢個同樣犯法！亦唔好畀政府有藉口取消選舉<br />\n我哋嘅目標只係要提醒市民受賄嘅法律風險<br />\n公公婆婆叔叔嬸嬸佢哋自己識諗<br />\n我哋冇可能杜絕所有賄選票<br />\n<br />\n3）重點<br />\n票站附近幾十米分別有「禁止拉票區」同埋「禁止逗留區」<br />\n「禁止逗留區」就冇得傾，唔可以喺嗰度派<br />\n但「禁止拉票區」呢，就手足們可以試下<br />\n因為我哋嘅行動唔係要幫人拉票，亦都唔係要阻止人哋投票<br />\n只係自發幫政府做宣傳，理論上冇可能犯法<br />\n但當然，今日嘅香港乜都有可能發生<br />\n所以手足亦無謂硬碰，有需要就行返遠少少先繼續<br />\n<br />\n4）自問和理非，生活好多包袱，一大堆原因上唔到前線嘅手足<br />\n今次行動完全合法<br />\n一定要企出嚟<br />\n最少都幫手影印多啲單張去派<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oa7eC5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOa7eC5b.jpg&h=53218f0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93fee08c4030e0ac51589c6ec2e8a609b539762e","tid":1747633,"uid":84632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0d396560a080da15fe2fa255ef8b84126f4b06","tid":1747633,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"【11-24 告急】 投本土泛民，不投建制，連登每小時245留言討論投對家，有圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScLG1qp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScLG1qp.png&h=c6d3bd0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezKeyS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezKeyS</a>"},{"pid":"4a5f8b1e0dbd0a9f7d4c1c2547ed0332b59461a3","tid":1747633,"uid":310858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7772dd7fee169c48df1e350f700eabba17d63a05","tid":1747633,"uid":4401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:34:14.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2024b2ad9d0a5f91e6de7d54e2d328d81c599c19","tid":1747633,"uid":84632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:37:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji